title: Tricked Up for Treats
description: Rusty Duchene signs up his fiancé, Sean Delahunt for a couples’ amateur drag competition. The prizes are awesome but the real prize, the one Rusty is hoping they will win is the prize of letting Sean be himself for a night.But the head game he’s playing with Sean comes with the high risk that Sean will fracture instead of become whole.If the worst happens, will Rusty be strong enough to hold their relationship together, or will this be the end of their long term love?
author: Chris   Cox
